# Local working extracts and intermediate staging.
data/processed/eia860*/

# ECWT release output CSVs (full results, scoped release, per-hour cold-tail
# provenance, and sources) are large and regenerate on every run, so they are
# published as GitHub Release assets rather than committed to Git history.
# See the README "Release outputs" section. The small *_SHA256SUMS.txt manifest
# stays in-repo so any downloaded Release asset can be verified, and the built
# dashboard under build/ stays in-repo as the viewable artifact.
data/processed/*.csv
